{"tid":2513293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"\"極多圖\"尖沙咀不忘老細威脅前員工,員工爆料","createTime":"2021-05-02T11:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T11:39:57.000Z","uid":337199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b15d94cbf17969916bf64e3fea9756bcff4c72","tid":2513293,"uid":337199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"我就係個前員工 事源係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQcrZe2fEX4cy2T1GFXXXY3bSh18WWhP72V7TD534jf4o?filename=J3X9WFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ3X9WFX.jpg&h=65504ef7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXL5Ruo5HScZ3hV4iZWXEArgAJCnF7qXWDU5eTQuzfWgM?filename=7VqvF7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VqvF7M.jpg&h=f0deeaeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以我就去咗勞工處到落案僱主拖欠薪金<br />\n向積金局追討返佢無交嘅強積金(佢有好多個月無供)<br />\n<span class=\"red\">結果佢就話要用我啲個人資料黎威脅我</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdqhq5MRzsvXZnVcE3buQ87Ust9sXD3bWRY7msddmGCBE?filename=kytxaW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkytxaW1.jpg&h=a9e66f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">佢不仁 我不義</span> <br />\n<strong>一</strong>,用大陸豬肉呃人係泰國豬肉<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd9hL2HttpW5ozCtutzXi42ew4H1vGka1sZv845Yn7QMC?filename=o92mNGa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo92mNGa.jpg&h=4a88e29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV7gqseUDPtu4jHYRwk42k8GK2JMZ6qWTriUosjUA9Djd?filename=M8TQF1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8TQF1a.jpg&h=ce656df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSVupduNN6pj7Zr1Xq5V3KM5mAC2feNgqhUpa6YjMM9yt?filename=q7zPWzw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq7zPWzw.jpg&h=76c7f5de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>二</strong>,<span class=\"red\">極多老鼠(大量老鼠圖慎點) </span> <br />\n由上年5月份開始就有老鼠嘅出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNbcPs6bXnyCZM2wvmJ3ZEpCaaWRgPBSQ4XRNtyGbL6Rm?filename=p4aPcKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp4aPcKH.jpg&h=2f378696&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXtyRYy7nNpwra1TaTUTrXYgvmNpMRtsm7Ui6SKLi7gNw?filename=bZb3hbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZb3hbm.jpg&h=8572294d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTo4uv5PyCrjV8vR3jrPtdZg4AbBBwtLqj8xymtVVn13Y?filename=MNqfSKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMNqfSKH.jpg&h=17844640&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQRZXVeAVVpdrH99z7S8WUSiegn9fdT7eEqvTXCfcBxzq?filename=y5H6eX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5H6eX1.jpg&h=4a429909&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTD9ZCPTVspt1LAMfZXehcis6WvkrmiKaWWby4UBDQ6Dm?filename=5QhNJRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QhNJRm.jpg&h=9a651319&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdnEGJbdazrPMvd58L9UeBQtrhp166Q519PYMqFwUtWzT?filename=5TDpL4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5TDpL4G.jpg&h=aabca09e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU1EdBfKD7dgCVw1osAZ4HMtRRaNcGvv3ahZBPdCgkrNJ?filename=9Gwe8h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Gwe8h1.jpg&h=3469784d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJVGOh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJVGOh2.jpg&h=a5e94eef&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYaYKeN4v3VZ25Cvm1gp9kPWm1HSmnWFCx2runW5ViQm7?filename=1dOhmC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dOhmC2.jpg&h=01231a2c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZGGpaNdSd51btRUqjPbuKxYRqUr5gzu6mwraENGZ9ihp?filename=6S3dEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6S3dEpG.jpg&h=9a3825ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i2qzoRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi2qzoRm.jpg&h=84d4d85e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpLGOh1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpLGOh1.jpg&h=c0494f02&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2ugCbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2ugCbk.jpg&h=6cd65ed0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2H9Xbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2H9Xbm.jpg&h=1ba202f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3u4L4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3u4L4G.jpg&h=efe8ecb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9iLvGC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9iLvGC1.jpg&h=28b8cda3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cHeoRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cHeoRm.jpg&h=8c75fa42&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢個兜我當時係擲咗,但後尾我聽同事講,店長攞返起黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(個兜平時會攞黎撈餃子餡/食材)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KJ9cW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KJ9cW9.jpg&h=3568d0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3EDQKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3EDQKF.jpg&h=80866877&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>三</strong>,<span class=\"red\">老鼠屎</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oR16Zw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoR16Zw8.jpg&h=c5ae065c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AieXmLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAieXmLt.jpg&h=4647b529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oUsJYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oUsJYO.jpg&h=b32756ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPmCmLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPmCmLt.jpg&h=62054d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjcFjw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjcFjw8.jpg&h=5f66f9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axMSaDO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxMSaDO.jpg&h=a6ed9551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOx9XiO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOx9XiO.jpg&h=fd8c763e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcQfSR8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcQfSR8.jpg&h=9f3010a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcNNJYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcNNJYO.jpg&h=6b5fb679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwhFjw8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwhFjw8.jpg&h=eb063eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zdhmSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zdhmSf.jpg&h=4261ffe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMVjAcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMVjAcf.jpg&h=92da592c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直有向老細反映老鼠問題,但佢一直都係得過且過就算,完全無認真正視過問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRb6ZrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRb6ZrO.jpg&h=37a2713c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直到有一次朝早有兩枱客人食緊野嘅時候,有隻老鼠彈咗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇到個客彈起身,即刻比錢走人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/goZo1GD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgoZo1GD.jpg&h=10580516&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢件事之後我同同事上網搵咗滅鼠公司,情況先開始有改善<br />\n<span class=\"red\">以上所有老鼠圖,全部都有send過比老細睇</span><br />\n <br />\n<strong>四</strong>,另外相信近一兩個月有黎過堂食嘅朋友都會聞到一陣陣嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,因為雪櫃由後巷搬咗出黎,而個雪櫃係唔凍嘅,所以放係雪櫃入面嘅肉類會出血水變壞,之後發出惡臭味,<br />\n但會繼續用,比啲客食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,包括你哋飲緊佢講所謂嘅無味精雞湯(其實係會落大量雞粉)嘅湯骨同雞,<br />\n腸粉用嘅肥牛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6kMuXqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6kMuXqW.jpg&h=dcd17d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTULP2KMuC7CoPjdqg3nLzLQ4qBS1TUYBcogXCSFUcjBg?filename=HJkcaLV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJkcaLV.jpg&h=a5b0f7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sFOX6jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsFOX6jf.jpg&h=e47628a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWviCcp2urHDj6kSVKerjMmATVrdBFznnNx1CRBaLreDT?filename=7TuMfc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TuMfc6.jpg&h=091636eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有基本上舖頭7成嘅野都係淘寶/大陸野<br />\n包括生餃嘅12格,18格環保盒,辣椒醬玻璃樽,雪櫃,鐵兜,豬肉丸,牛肉丸,等等都係<br />\n<br />\n最後佢講過當佢哋只係一間不是藍的食店,用意係咩,大家自己諗<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmc7MQopn8LXSPdC841G7cxSytwCuxhDwUSdqy7AM6hpzC?filename=V8nFjL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8nFjL1.jpg&h=9f975142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">以上句句屬實,唔通我離職後,追討返屬於我嘅野,就要受你嘅威脅?<br />\n我絕不妥協</span>"},{"pid":"c3da3408073bff08e8f27eaef826a3b85e27c863","tid":2513293,"uid":337199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"推"}]}